== Short Bio 
~~~
I am majoring in mathematics at [https://www.sysu.edu.cn/sysuen/ Sun Yat-Sen University(SYSU,中山大学)] and am expected to graduate in 2025.
~~~

== Research Interests 
~~~
My research interests broadly lie at the interface of *optimization*, *statistics* and *operations research*, with a focus on their applications in *data-driven decision-making* and *machine learning*
- Stochastic and Non-Convex Optimization
- Causal Inference and Experiment Design
- Differential Privacy
- Learning Theory

~~~




